Good morning Atlanta!!

For those who came out to the conference, thank you!!

For those who want a May event, we have one with Colleen who’s supplying _baseball tickets_, as seen above posted by Kai.

Have a great weekend and assuming finals are over, go catch up on sleep!!

Except to those graduating... go graduate! Congratulations graduates of 2023. :clap: :mortar_board: :clap:

---> Also congratulations to some from our Atlanta group: <@U02L4D90KD0> and <@U02EEGFEYHH>
Post pictures if you see them, or other graduates!!

Go jackets!!
